title: Classmate, Kamimura Yuuka wa Kou Itta. Vol 02 Ch 025
text: Read Classmate, Kamimura Yuuka wa Kou Itta. Manga Online Shirasaki is incredibly bored by his unchanging daily school life and he ends up falling for his weird classmate Kamimura Yuuka, who rants about changing the world to his uninterested classmates. However, when she reveals the truth about the nature of their world to him, everything will quickly become stranger than he would ever have expected!
